              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <p>'Absence of good'</p><p>There's no bad, which is only the absence of good. Thus, bad is just 'imperfection'. I always believe that there are no good and bad, cuz it's hard to determine and define. </p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p42256412-1.jpg"></div></div>
